{"action": "input", "code": "def sort_colors_by_position(color_list: List[int], color_position_list: List[int]) -> List[int]:\n    return [color for _, color in sorted(zip(color_position_list, color_list))]\ndef paint_columns(sorted_color_list: List[int], max_color_num_list: List[int]) -> np.ndarray:\n    output = np.zeros((max(max_color_num_list), len(sorted_color_list)))\n    for i, color in enumerate(sorted_color_list):\n        output[:max_color_num_list[i], i] = color\n    return output\ndef find_leftmost_position(input_grid: np.ndarray, color: int) -> int:\n    for i in range(input_grid.shape[1]):\n        if color in input_grid[:, i]:\n            return i\n    return -1\ndef main(input_grid: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    color_list = get_colors(input_grid)\n    color_num_list = count_colors(input_grid, color_list)\n    color_position_list = find_leftmost_position(input_grid, color_list)\n    max_color_list, max_color_num_list = compare_colors(color_list, color_num_list)\n    sorted_color_list = sort_colors_by_position(max_color_list, color_position_list)\n    output = paint_columns(sorted_color_list, max_color_num_list)\n    return output\ndef get_colors(input_grid: np.ndarray) -> List[int]:\n    return list(set(input_grid.flatten()))[1:]\ndef count_colors(input_grid: np.ndarray, color_list: List[int]) -> List[int]:\n    color_num_list = []\n    for color in color_list:\n        color_num_list.append(np.count_nonzero(input_grid == color))\n    return color_num_list\ndef compare_colors(color_list: List[int], color_num_list: List[int]) -> Tuple[List[int], List[int]]:\n    max_color_list = []\n    max_color_num_list = []\n    max_color_num = max(color_num_list)\n    for i in range(len(color_list)):\n        if color_num_list[i] == max_color_num:\n            max_color_list.append(color_list[i])\n            max_color_num_list.append(color_num_list[i])\n    return (max_color_list, max_color_num_list)", "user_code": "def main(input_grid: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n\tcolor_list = `get all color in input grid except black`(input_grid)\n\tcolor_num_list = `count the number of Corresponding color in input_grid`(input_grid,color_list)\n\tcolor_position_list = `find the leftmost position for Corresponding color in input_grid`(input_grid,color_list)\n\tmax_color_list,max_color_num_list = `compare the number of these colors to come up with the most numerous and equal colors`(color_list,color_num_list) \n\tsorted_color_list = `sort the color list by the order of leftmost_position from small to big`(max_color_list,color_position_list)\n\toutput = `paint one col per sorted_color, the number of row is the number of this color point`(sorted_color_list,max_color_num_list)\n\treturn output\n\t", "gpt_code": "def sort_colors_by_position(color_list: List[int], color_position_list: List[int]) -> List[int]:\n    return [color for _, color in sorted(zip(color_position_list, color_list))]\ndef paint_columns(sorted_color_list: List[int], max_color_num_list: List[int]) -> np.ndarray:\n    output = np.zeros((max(max_color_num_list), len(sorted_color_list)))\n    for i, color in enumerate(sorted_color_list):\n        output[:max_color_num_list[i], i] = color\n    return output\ndef find_leftmost_position(input_grid: np.ndarray, color: int) -> int:\n    for i in range(input_grid.shape[1]):\n        if color in input_grid[:, i]:\n            return i\n    return -1\ndef get_colors(input_grid: np.ndarray) -> List[int]:\n    return list(set(input_grid.flatten()))[1:]\ndef count_colors(input_grid: np.ndarray, color_list: List[int]) -> List[int]:\n    color_num_list = []\n    for color in color_list:\n        color_num_list.append(np.count_nonzero(input_grid == color))\n    return color_num_list\ndef compare_colors(color_list: List[int], color_num_list: List[int]) -> Tuple[List[int], List[int]]:\n    max_color_list = []\n    max_color_num_list = []\n    max_color_num = max(color_num_list)\n    for i in range(len(color_list)):\n        if color_num_lis